summary: This document is a certification from the Secretary of State of Delaware, Michael Harkins, confirming the incorporation of Hypertoil, Inc. on July 18, 1991. It serves as an official record of the incorporation and includes details about the filing time and associated fees.

persons.name: Michael Harkins
persons.context: Michael Harkins certifies the attached document as a true and correct copy of the certificate of incorporation for Hypertoil, Inc.

events.title: Incorporation of Hypertoil, Inc.
events.description: Hypertoil, Inc. was officially incorporated in Delaware.

keyFacts: The document certifies the incorporation of Hypertoil, Inc. on July 18, 1991.
Michael Harkins is the Secretary of State who certified the document.
The filing was completed at 2:30 PM.
A state document fee of $4.00 was paid.
The document is marked as confidential.
